Package jade.domain.DFGUIManagement

Class DFAppletOntology

java.lang.Object
jade.content.onto.Ontology
jade.domain.DFGUIManagement.DFAppletOntology
All Implemented Interfaces:
DFAppletVocabulary, ExceptionVocabulary, FIPAManagementVocabulary, Serializable
public class DFAppletOntology extends Ontology implements DFAppletVocabulary
This class represents the ontology DFApplet-management , containing all JADE extensions related to applet management. There is only a single instance of this class.

The package contains one class for each Frame in the ontology.
